      </li>
      <li class="js-actionMomentMakerCreateMoment">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Add to new Moment</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Good project: Help <a href="https://twitter.com/bilalghalib" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="16154713"><s>@</s><b>bilalghalib</b></a> and Mitch Altman set up a <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/hackerspace?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>hackerspace</b></a> movement in Africa <a href="http://t.co/HTfXDIg6" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://kck.st/pqyJzL" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://kck.st/pqyJzL"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">kck.st/pqyJzL</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/makerfaire?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b><strong>makerfaire</strong></b></a></p>

            Report Tweet
        </button>
      </li>
      <li class="dropdown-divider"></li>
      <li class="js-actionMomentMakerAddTweetToOtherMoment MomentMakerAddTweetToOtherMoment">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Add to other Moment</button>
      </li>
      <li class="js-actionMomentMakerCreateMoment">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Add to new Moment</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Insanely cool hack behind Chumby's NETV, to insert content into HDMI stream w/o decryting it: <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/makerfaire?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b><strong>makerfaire</strong></b></a>  <a href="http://t.co/VEBAl3ol" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://pulse.me/s/1HEHY" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://pulse.me/s/1HEHY"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">pulse.me/s/1HEHY</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a></p>

          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Unblock <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>OReillyMedia</b></span></button>
        </li>
      <li class="report-link js-actionReport" data-nav="report">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">
          
            
            Report Tweet
        </button>
      </li>
      <li class="dropdown-divider"></li>

          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Unblock <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>TreeHugger</b></span></button>
        </li>
      <li class="report-link js-actionReport" data-nav="report">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">
          
            
            Report Tweet
        </button>
      </li>
      <li class="dropdown-divider"></li>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
          <li class="mute-user-item"><button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Mute <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>donttrythis</b></span></button></li>
    <li class="unmute-user-item"><button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Unmute <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>donttrythis</b></span></button></li>

        <li class="block-link js-actionBlock" data-nav="block">

            Report Tweet

          <li class="mute-user-item"><button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Mute <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>exploratorium</b></span></button></li>
    <li class="unmute-user-item"><button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Unmute <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>exploratorium</b></span></button></li>

        <li class="block-link js-actionBlock" data-nav="block">
          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Block <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>exploratorium</b></span></button>
        </li>
        <li class="unblock-link js-actionUnblock" data-nav="unblock">
          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Unblock <span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>exploratorium</b></span></button>
        </li>
      <li class="report-link js-actionReport" data-nav="report">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">
          
            
            Report Tweet
        </button>
      </li>
      <li class="dropdown-divider"></li>

        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Add to other Moment</button>

  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Free tickets to <a href="https://twitter.com/makerfaire" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1578141"><s>@</s><b><strong>MakerFaire</strong></b></a> in San Mateo,CA on May 21, 22-teach knit, crochet, stitch <a href="https://twitter.com/TNNAorg" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="34622363"><s>@</s><b>TNNAorg</b></a> needlearts booth - email tnnamaker@gmail now!</p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">May have something to do with the glares I get when I mention <a href="https://twitter.com/makerfaire" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1578141"><s>@</s><b><strong>makerfaire</strong></b></a> to Austinites.
